data.description: $$$15k in Seller concessions with full price offer of $615k.$$$ Come take a peek at this beautiful little cottage. The backyard is an entertainers dream with a tri-level deck, built it firepit, mature trees, above ground pool and inflatable hot tub. On almost a full acre lot. Shop with power, heat, insulation, shower, sink, kitchen area. Storage shed. Plenty of room for RV parking, trailers, haulers, ATV, Boats, whatever you need space for. No HOA and CC&Rs. Property is also located on a dead-end street.  New roof in 2016. New HVAC/Gas water heater in 2020. All new exterior paint, interior paint, LVP flooring, light fixtures, and remodeled bathrooms in 2022. Assumable VA loan interest rate @ 4.25% Buyers will have to pay closing costs and agent fees. Only VA eligible can assume this loan.
